              "key": "4c1c4367-316b-4c80-a046-3080d92d9517",
              "title": null,
              "semantic_type": "TextAtom",
              "is_public": true,
              "text": "## Takeaways\n\n- be clear about the cost of a transaction\n- let the user know that, if the transaction fails due to a missing requirement, they might not get the full transaction back",
              "instructor_notes": ""
